        <item>
            <title>1.11.2</title>
            <pubDate>Tue, 28 Apr 2026 17:15:41 +0900</pubDate>
            <link>https://github.com/Saqoosha/Canopy</link>
            <sparkle:version>37</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.11.2</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>15.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <sparkle:hardwareRequirements>arm64</sparkle:hardwareRequirements>
            <description sparkle:format="markdown"><![CDATA[### Bug Fixes
- Clicking the Dock icon after closing all windows no longer brings back the previous session view. Closed sessions now stay closed; the Dock click opens a fresh launcher window. ([#46](https://github.com/Saqoosha/Canopy/pull/46))
- Window state is no longer restored across app launches, so a session window that was explicitly closed in the previous run won't resurrect on the next launch.
]]></description>
